Bunch of random scripts that try to build an "Action Dataset" (Action oriented instead of being video / type oriented)

* Build_action_dataset concatinates all the action instances from the segementation transcripts.
* main_clutering_filtering is a script that tries to. 
	- Filter out useless actions.
	-	Cluster Similar actions using:
		* Word embedings. 
		* LLMs for large action sets after word embedings. (From our testing word embedings tend to group some set of actions together too much.) 
	- Combine successive clips of the same action.

* FilteredClipDownloader Downloads all the videos that are needed, and de-duplicates clips that get used at multiple points

Requirements
-----------
yt-dlp
ffmpeg
rich
sentence_transformers
transformer



Installation / Instructions 
---------------------------
Call the scripts in order (some steps may be interchangable, and please look at the code! Some parts have been commented out at various stages.

